title: CPAC crowd cheers missing vaccination goal. Hear Dr. Fauci's response
description: Dr. Anthony Fauci calls the reaction by the crowd at the Conservative Political Action Committee to a conservative author's comments about the US falling short of it's vaccination goal 'horrifying.'

title: Watch fans go crazy in Rome
description: Italy clinched its first major title for 15 years with a penalty shootout win over England in the Euro 2020 final at London's Wembley Stadium.

title: Branson's advice to Bezos after historic space flight
description: CNN's Rachel Crane speaks with Virgin Galactic founder Richard Branson after his historic trip to space.
